text: Kampong Batang Mitus (Malay for Batang Mitus Village) is a village situated in the eastern part of Tutong District, Brunei, within the mukim of Kiudang. The acting incumbent village head is Abdul Rahim bin Abdullah Yakin, who is also the penghulu of the mukim. It has the postcode TE2543. == References == Batang Mitus
